official_title: SIBTime: Media-enhanced Technology for Promoting the Behavioral Health and Family Relationships of Typically Developing Young Siblings
inclusion_criteria:
Criteria:

Inclusion criteria:

1. Parent of a child with a disability and a typically developing child aged 3-6
2. Has a smartphone or tablet
3. Speaks English or Spanish

Exclusion criteria:

1. None
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
